>{{cite web |title=李義祥爆違法兼任工地主任　台鐵認了！「3單位」疏失釀大禍 |url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210404/1953240.htm |website=ETtoday新聞雲 |accessdate=2021-04-04 |date=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404105942/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210404/1953240.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，李義祥曾在2018年當選[[民主進步黨|民主進步黨]]花蓮縣黨代表，2020年由於任期屆滿而卸任，之後因未繳黨費使其黨籍處在停權中<ref>{{cite web |title=有黨證！民進黨證實：李義祥曾任花蓮縣黨代表 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/122094/5364350 |website=聯合新聞網 |accessdate=2021-04-04 |date=2021-04-03 |archive-date=2021-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403163323/https://udn.com/news/story/122094/5364350 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=【台鐵出軌】李義祥遭起底曾任民進黨代表　推薦入黨的縣黨部前執委也因偽造施工圖齊被訴 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210405/SPGFZ33H6RH77EUUQ2XR2RQHJA/ |website=蘋果日報 |accessdate=2021-04-05 |date=2021-04-05 |archive-date=2021-04-05 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210405025324/https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210405/SPGFZ33H6RH77EUUQ2XR2RQHJA/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2021年4月2日，李義祥因其疏失造成TEMU1000型電聯車事故，同月[[民主進步黨|民主進步黨]]花蓮縣黨部提案開除李義祥黨籍；5月5日，民進黨中評會通過開除李義祥黨籍。<ref>{{cite web |title=太魯閣事件元凶李義祥　民進黨中評會今確認開除黨籍 |url=https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20210505inv008/ |website=鏡傳媒 |accessdate=2021-05-06 |date=2021-05-05 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509053421/https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20210505inv008/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=太魯閣包商李義祥 民進黨中評會今確認開除黨籍 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3522367 |website=自由時報 |accessdate=2021-05-06 |date=2021-05-05 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506131724/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3522367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

